Yes. Oh they - at least made a wee plate of broth, put a broth that probably last two days. Aye, and you had a meat and - the meat you had then, if you had meat - it would be in the broth. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12071385 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7550569\charrsid10909046 Did you have anything else?
