Well it all depended. If they - if they'd been lucky - you would get fish, you know, from the - fish shop. Mother had to put them all you know and - otherwise we might have had a sausage. Well I wouldna sau sausages, I'd say a sausage.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12071385 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7550569\charrsid10909046 It was always something cooked?
