Yes, went to - the Lyceum now and again and the theatre and the concerts, oh yes. And the Empire. Used to wait for them come out - for them coming out for to go for a drink at nine o'cloc
k you see it gives you a time check, see when they're coming back again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12071385 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7550569\charrsid10909046 Did you ever get any pocket money?
