Well it seems to be in - you see, they never locked their doors against anybody like that, you just walked in sort of business and - anybody - kids were ill or anything they all helped each other. Or if the mother was ill one wo
uld take the wash and do that and - one would would scrub the floor or - you know - all the neighbours knew each other and knew their circumstances and so on. Aye, helped each other.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12071385 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7550569\charrsid10909046 What about when your younger brothers and sister were born, did the
 neighbours come in to help then?
