Oh yes, oh yes. Bar one uncle which - seemed to be very uppish so we didn't see him so often. All the other ones was quite - like myself, quite
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12071385 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7550569\charrsid10909046 You visited each other?
