Oh yes. You see, a recruit in the peacetime Army, wasna wartime, he must get a first class certificate of education, and site for his second one. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12071385 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7550569\charrsid10909046 They actually gave you an education in the Army as well?
