Oh well - my mother would get me the job but she would be in for a ha'penny or a penn'orth of milk and - probably they'd say, I would need a laddie for - going round to customers with - and mind you it was all cans.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12071385 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7550569\charrsid10909046 What exactly did you have to do, did you go early in the morning?
