Oh yes, used to go out in the evenings, there used to be a nice wee picture housed own in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Arum Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} called {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
